Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:49.49,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{NOTE:この絆珠は正式にお前にやるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:52.24,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{NOTE:頑張ってお前も修業するダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.75,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,{NOTE:修業？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.04,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ちょっと！}
