Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:30.41,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ふむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:35.12,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ならばお前らもこれを持って雪山に行くダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.79,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{NOTE:これが絆珠。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.96,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{NOTE:奇麗…}
